  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal is to establish the practical usefulness of vestibular stimulation for modulating
      pain perception and to describe the possible mechanisms that could underlie neural
      vestibular-somatosensory interactions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
